&lt;/div>&lt;p>실제로 데이터베이스를 보면 {참조하는 관계명} _ {참조하는 관계명}으로 이뤄져 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://d7mekz.github.io/p/entgo-ent-orm/img2.png"
width="1012"
height="254"
srcset="https://d7mekz.github.io/p/entgo-ent-orm/img2_huc30db4609febd34d8d470f3ce29d95a3_45097_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://d7mekz.github.io/p/entgo-ent-orm/img2_huc30db4609febd34d8d470f3ce29d95a3_45097_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="398"
data-flex-basis="956px"
